Thespians across east Africa as well as renowned filmmakers converged on Friday evening at Tune Hotel, Westlands for the Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards cocktail.Influencers in the entertainment industry had the chance to network as well as get to know how to submit their entries for the fifth edition of the awards.Among the personalities who showed up were scriptwriter Abel Mutua, actress Catherine Kamau, Phillip Karanja, Zamaradi Productions executive producer Appie Matere and Mnet Africa head of marketing Tiwa Medubi.